## Update Menu Item Details

This API endpoint is used to update the details of a specific menu item.

### Request

- Method: PATCH

- URL: `{{base_url}}/api/menu-items/{{item_id}}?format=json`

- Headers:

    - Content-Type: application/json

- Body:

    - title (string, required): The updated title of the menu item.

    - price (float, required): The updated price of the menu item.

    - featured (boolean, required): Indicates if the menu item is featured.

    - category (Int, required): The updated category of the menu item.

        - Available Categories:


| Category ID | Name |
| --- | --- |
| 1 | entree |
| 2 | beverage |
| 3 | side-order |
| 4 | dessert |

### Response

The response for this request is a JSON object with the following schema:

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "count": {
            "type": "integer"
        },
        "next": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "previous": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "results": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                    "item_id": {
                        "type": "integer"
                    },
                    "title": {
                        "type": "string"
                    },
                    "price": {
                        "type": "string"
                    },
                    "featured": {
                        "type": "boolean"
                    },
                    "category": {
                        "type": "string"
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

 ```

The response includes the count of items, pagination links, and an array of updated menu item details including the item_id, title, price, featured, and category.

