### Retrieve Menu Items

This endpoint makes an HTTP GET request to retrieve a list of menu items in JSON format.

#### Request

The request does not require a request body. It retrieves menu items using the following endpoint:

`GET /api/menu-items/?format=json`

#### Response

The response will be a JSON object representing the menu items, following the schema below:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "count": {
      "type": "integer"
    },
    "next": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "previous": {
      "type": "null"
    },
    "results": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "product_sku": {
            "type": "integer"
          },
          "category": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "product_name": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "price_per_item": {
            "type": "integer"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

This endpoint retrieves details of a specific menu item identified by its `item_id`.

## Request

### Request URL

- Method: GET

- URL: `{{base_url}}/api/menu-items/{{item_id}}?format=json`


### Request Body

This request does not require a request body.

## Response

### Response Body

The response is in JSON format and includes the following fields:

- `product_sku`(number): The unique identifier of the menu item.

- `product_name` (string): The title or name of the menu item.

- `price_per_item` (string): The price of the menu item.

- `featured` (boolean): Indicates whether the menu item is featured

- `on_sale` (boolean): Indicates whether the menu item is on sale.

- `category` (string): The category to which the menu item belongs.

- `nutritional_facts` (object): Contains the nutritonal value data of the menu item

    - `calories`(number): The number of calories of the menu item measured in calorie.

    - `sugar` (number): The number of grams of sugar in the menu item.

    - `protein` (number): The number of grams of protein in the menu item.

    - `carbohydrates` (number): The number of milligrams of carbohydrates inthe menu item.

    - `saturated_fat` (number): TThe number of grams of saturated fat in the menu item.

- `allergens` (object): Contains common food allegens of the menu item

    - `contains_dairy` (boolean): Indicates whether the menu item contains milk or dairy ingredients.

    - `contains_gluten` (boolean): Indicates whether the menu item contains gluten-based ingredients.

    - `contains_treenuts` (boolean): Indicates whether the menu item contains treenut ingredients.


### JSON Schema

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "product_sku": {
            "type": "number"
        },
        "category": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "product_name": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "price_per_item": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "featured": {
            "type": "boolean"
        },
        "on_sale": {
            "type": "boolean"
        },
        "nutritional_facts": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
                "calories": {
                    "type": "number"
                },
                "sugar": {
                    "type": "string"
                },
                "protein": {
                    "type": "string"
                },
                "carbohydrates": {
                    "type": "string"
                },
                "saturated_fat": {
                    "type": "string"
                }
            }
        },
        "allergens": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
                "contains_dairy": {
                    "type": "boolean"
                },
                "contains_gluten": {
                    "type": "boolean"
                },
                "contains_treenuts": {
                    "type": "boolean"
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

 ```

